  // 1 = single-axis) and FStruct[1] is pAxis. The no-arg form keeps FStruct[0]=0
  // so its serialized string is byte-identical to earlier versions.
  // Use case: flatten a (1,N,1)/(N,1,1) shape back to a plain feature vector.
  // Coded by Claude (AI).
